      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and internal patch tests confirm correct implementation of linear hexahedral and tetrahedral elements. Order-of-convergence tests performed on representative sub-models."
    },
    {
