      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic isotropic titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) material model appropriate for sub-yield loading regime. Geometric nonlinearity included. Contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation at screw-rod interface."
