    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team accepted this gap given the constrained regulatory timeline and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. Overall credibility is judged sufficient for Medium model risk.",
